WEBVTT

00:00:00.001 --> 00:00:03.021
"Fruit"

00:00:03.647 --> 00:00:07.027
(Episode 7: Gap)

00:00:23.166 --> 00:00:24.698
Can't this kid

00:00:24.698 --> 00:00:26.400
just keep her head down?

00:01:12.966 --> 00:01:15.800
Make sure to see a doctor,

00:01:15.800 --> 00:01:17.066
check that nothing's broken.

00:01:18.166 --> 00:01:19.666
I'll take care of Chips.

00:01:21.031 --> 00:01:22.730
Then...

00:01:22.730 --> 00:01:24.529
Chips,

00:01:24.529 --> 00:01:26.433
you be good, okay?

00:01:27.866 --> 00:01:30.600
I'll be going now, Miss.

00:01:32.133 --> 00:01:33.066
Thank you.

00:02:15.200 --> 00:02:16.700
I am her teacher.

00:02:17.466 --> 00:02:18.833
Don't cross the line...

00:02:22.866 --> 00:02:24.000
But...

00:02:25.333 --> 00:02:26.966
the real crossing of the line

00:02:28.133 --> 00:02:30.581
is me pretending that nothing happened.